## Project Structure

```
AI Hackathon/
├── backend/
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── database.py      — SQLite + SQLAlchemy setup
│   │   ├── models.py        — User + Case models
│   │   ├── schemas.py       — Pydantic schemas (Create/Update/Response)
│   │   ├── crud.py          — CRUD with filtering/sorting/search
│   │   ├── constants.py     — Dropdown options (7 lists)
│   │   ├── auth.py          — JWT auth, password hashing, reset
│   │   ├── analytics.py     — Aggregation queries (8 endpoints)
│   │   ├── ranking.py       — Scoring engine + AI analysis
│   │   ├── agent.py         — Solution design agent
│   │   └── main.py          — FastAPI app with all endpoints
│   ├── requirements.txt
│   └── seed_data.py         — Sample data + admin user
├── frontend/
│   └── index.html           — Single-file React + Ant Design app
├── .gitignore
└── README.md
```

## Running the App

```
cd "AI Hackathon/backend"
py seed_data.py              # First time only
py -m uvicorn app.main:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000
```

Open http://127.0.0.1:8000/ — Login as admin/admin123 or register a new account.

